quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  29,15,phir hum ne Nooh ko aur kashti walon ko nijaat di aur kashti ko ahal aalam ke liye nishani bana diya
  29,16,aur ibrahim ko ( yaad karo ) jab onhon ne apni qoum se kaha ke khuda ki ibadat karo aur is se daro agar tum samajh rakhtay ho to yeh tumahray haq mein behtar hai
  29,17,to tum khuda ko chore kar buton ko pujte aur tufaan bandhte ho to jin logon ko tum khuda ke siwa pujte ho woh tum ko rizaq dainay ka ikhtiyar nahi rakhtay pas khuda hi ke haan se rizaq talab karo aur isi ki ibadat karo aur isi ka shukar karo isi ki taraf tum lout kar jao ge
  29,18,aur agar tum ( meri ) takzieeb karo to tum se pehlay bhi ummatain ( apne payghambaroon ki ) takzieeb krchki hain. aur paighambar ke zimmay khol kar suna dainay ke siwa aur kuch nahi
  29,19,kiya onhon ne nahi dekha ke khuda kis terhan khalqat ko pehli baar peda karta phir ( kis terhan ) is ko baar baar peda karta rehta hai. yeh khuda ko aasaan hai
  29,20,keh do ke malik mein chalo phiro aur dekho ke is ne kis terhan khalqat ko pehli dafaa pedakiya hai phir khuda hi pichli paidaiesh peda kere ga. be shak khuda har cheez par Qadir hai
  29,21,woh jisay chahay azaab day aur jis par chahay reham kere. aur usi ki taraf tum lout’tay jao ge
  29,22,aur tum ( uss ko ) nah zameen mein aajiz kar saktay ho nah aasman mein aur nah khuda ke siwa tumhara koi dost hai aur nah madadgaar
  29,23,aur jin logon ne khuda ki aayton se aur is ke milnay se inkaarkiya woh meri rehmat se na umeed hogaye hain aur un ko dard dainay wala azaab hoga
